Version: [1.0.0] Developer: KingsLink Devs Release Date: 28th August, 2023 Website: KingsLinkDevs.org Contact: kingslinkdevs@gmail.com
Description: Ultimate Text is a simple and user-friendly text editing application designed to provide a smooth and efficient writing experience. Whether you're a student, professional, or casual writer, Ultimate Text offers a range of features to help you create and edit text documents with ease.
Key Features: - Intuitive and clutter-free interface - Customizable font and color options - Support for various file formats, including TXT and more - Quick and easy text formatting and editing tools - Autosave and backup options for worry-free work - Keyboard shortcuts for faster navigation
We appreciate your support and feedback as we continue to improve Ultimate Text and provide you with a reliable tool for your writing needs.
Thank you for choosing Ultimare Text !
